CreateHubSecretRequest.description: Request model for creating a new hub secret.

agent_id.title: Agent Id
agent_id.description: The name or identifier of the agent to use to execute this run. Either `agent_id` or `assistant_id` must be provided.

assistant_id.title: Assistant Id
assistant_id.description: An OpenAI compatibility alias for agent. The ID of the [assistant](/docs/api-reference/assistants) to use to execute this run.

thread_id.title: Thread Id
thread_id.description: The thread to write messages to. If no thread is provided, an empty thread will be created.

new_message.title: New Message
new_message.description: A message to add to the thread before running the agents.

max_iterations.title: Max Iterations
max_iterations.description: Allow an agent to run for up to this number of iterations.

record_run.title: Record Run
record_run.description: Whether to record the run in the registry.

tool_resources.title: Tool Resources
tool_resources.description: A dictionary of tool resources to use for the run.

user_env_vars.title: User Env Vars
user_env_vars.description: Env vars provided by the user
